    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >领养专属3D桌宠，给桌面添上一抹治愈颜色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《崽物语Cubs Story》是一款3D桌宠挂机放置游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以领养专属桌宠崽崽，为它搭配漂亮套装、布置温馨风景，收获独一无二的陪伴时光。游戏结合换装、种植、职业养成、家园装扮等趣味休闲玩法，给你轻松萌趣的挂机体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟崽崽的互动：戳戳摸摸触发可爱反应！举高高也没问题哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/f157e03f048cc36b2985207df25375a8.poster.avif?t=1758202033\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/f157e03f048cc36b2985207df25375a8.webm?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/f157e03f048cc36b2985207df25375a8.mp4?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >给崽崽的新装：服装、发型、瞳色皆可自由搭配，每天都是穿搭秀！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/be016b1e94d160ab71d7e5544fccd8fe.poster.avif?t=1758202033\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/be016b1e94d160ab71d7e5544fccd8fe.webm?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/be016b1e94d160ab71d7e5544fccd8fe.mp4?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看崽崽的院子：解锁各种绿植、花卉、景观，布置你桌面的清新家园！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/71929365a6168805ec2c2f74947effcb.poster.avif?t=1758202033\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/71929365a6168805ec2c2f74947effcb.webm?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/71929365a6168805ec2c2f74947effcb.mp4?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和崽崽的成长：好崽崽会自己浇水，好植物会乖乖长大，解放双手才是真的休闲！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/a8cd2bd3f5d3b06a9ee9c410a3665086.poster.avif?t=1758202033\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/a8cd2bd3f5d3b06a9ee9c410a3665086.webm?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/a8cd2bd3f5d3b06a9ee9c410a3665086.mp4?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多日常等你解锁……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >崽崽饿了？喂它好吃的！崽崽也想摸鱼？整点好玩的！这是什么？虫子？抓一下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/94b00480642ddea1c9d3ef16aef85d7a.poster.avif?t=1758202033\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/94b00480642ddea1c9d3ef16aef85d7a.webm?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/94b00480642ddea1c9d3ef16aef85d7a.mp4?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/80576ffca878ffc4ed0588ffd0cfbc23.poster.avif?t=1758202033\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/80576ffca878ffc4ed0588ffd0cfbc23.webm?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/80576ffca878ffc4ed0588ffd0cfbc23.mp4?t=1758202033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《崽物语Cubs Story 》希望能为你的日常生活带来一丝放松与欢乐。无论是忙碌时的短暂互动，还是闲暇时的精心照料，这只桌宠崽崽都会成为你屏幕里永不掉线的陪伴！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285900/extras/61dcdd1d6ff5a6dcdb3f1e487a357b84.avif?t=1758202033\" width=620 height=259 /></span></p>",
